@noindent 
Command-line options:

@table @code
@item --bison-trace
Prints information generated by GNU Bison 
for tracing which parser rules are reduced 
and the state of the Bison stack. 

@item --multithread-input
Enables the use of multiple threads for input.

@item --multithread-output
Enables the use of multiple threads for output.

@item --multithread-include
Enables the use of multiple threads for input files included in other input
files.

@item --silent
Suppresses almost all output to standard output and standard error.

@item --quiet
Suppresses some output to standard output and standard error.

@item --verbose
Causes status information to be printed to standard output.

@item --help
Prints a help message and exits.

@item --version
Prints version information and exits.
@end table

